<headline>Special Weather Statement issued May 20 at 5:14AM MDT  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Light snow to affect Southwest MT this morning...
Expect an area of light snow to move southward through
Southwest MT this morning.
Snow accumulations on mountain passes will occur. Total snow
accumulations of another inch or so are expected before 9 AM.
Visibility will be reduced to less than one mile at times.
Those planning on traveling over mountain passes in Southwest MT
through this morning should be alert for quickly changing road
conditions.</description>
